article_id:64,category_name:News,title_name:Getherwing Limit-Increase Compensation[Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>At approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540879200"></span>, we will be implementing the following changes to Getherwing recovery.<br><br>・Getherwings earned upon leveling up will increase from 6 to 12<br>・Getherwings recovered using Wyrmite and Diamantium will increase from 6 to 12<br>・Getherwings obtained from the 30-day pack (Recovery) will increase from 6 to 12<br><br>We will be distributing Blessed Ethon Ashes as a gift to players compensating the difference of Getherwings recovered prior to this update in the following cases:<br><br>・Getherwings earned upon leveling up<br>・Getherwings recovered using Wyrmite and Diamantium<br>・Getherwings obtained from the 30-Day Pack (Recovery)<br><br>These gifts will be sent from Wednesday, Oct 31.<br>This notice will be updated once they have been distributed.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Updated <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540956600"></span>]</strong></span><br>The items were sent out at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540953000"></span>. You can claim them from your goodies box. These must be claimed by <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1541656799"></span>.</div><div><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1540879200,update_time1542363904